                                <div class="slider-box">
                                    <h6>Goedkoopste van <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0563/8412/7158/files/nederland-icon_0c786eeb-706b-472d-877a-7e88eaa17aa6.svg?v=1750160316" alt="" /> Nederland & <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0563/8412/7158/files/belgie-icon_587292f0-ae96-4df8-abcd-212eff6f7435.svg?v=1750160378" alt="" /> België</h6>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="slider-box">
